These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: pear, watermelon
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, video-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery
1. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person eating watermelon##8
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | water      |
| Food          | watermelon | pear    |
| Hobby         | video-games   | writing |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | mystery      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, journalist
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, van
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
3. the journalist is not to the right of the freelancer##8
4. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person who's hobby is reading##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | juice        | tea    |
| Hobby       | camping         | reading |
| Job         | journalist | freelancer   |
| Transport   | quad-bike               | van  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, disco
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, dutch
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the dutch is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
3. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure       | crime |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | disco    |
| Nationality   | russian | dutch |
| Pet           | hedgehog        | mouse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, scientist
There are 2 different nationalities: british, egyptian
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus
1. the british is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | rock-climbing  |
| Job           | scientist  | project-manager |
| Nationality   | egyptian | british   |
| Transport     | bus   | snowmobile |

