The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, nurse
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, scooter
1. the person eating pepper is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
2. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
3. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
4. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
5. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person eating peas##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | pepper | peas            |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | hiking              |
| Job         | teacher  | nurse |
| Transport   | bus     | scooter         |

