There are 2 different nationalities: french, chinese
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the french is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person driving the van is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person driving the van##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
